data.description: Check out this great Rambler in Clearfield. Home is at the end of the street. Lots of space and storage around the home and in the garage. Nice backyard with walkout basement.   Appliances stay as well as the washer & dryer. on Jan 8, 2024 the sewer line was checked and was told everything looks good.   No blind offers! and Seller has requested no creative financing! Buyers and Agents to get their own independent measurements.
